Service Intelligence Insight Components

Service Intelligence components provide a key contact center performance metric that can easily be embedded where you need it.

Available in: Lightning Experience, Enterprise and Unlimited Editions

The combination of customer data, KPIs, and AI helps your service team improve operations and reduce costs.

Enable the Propensity to Escalate Insight Component
Modify the batch data transformation to integrate the Einstein predictive model.

Use the Propensity to Escalate Insight Component
See AI-powered insights that estimate the likelihood customers will escalate their cases.

Use the Customer Effort Score Insight Component
Add to case page layouts so agents can see how much effort the customer is putting into the case.

Use the Time to Resolve Insight Component
Give agents AI-powered insights that estimate how much time it takes to resolve cases.

Determine whether you're meeting your customer service goals with an easy-to-understand metric in Service Intelligence insights.
title: Service Intelligence Insight Components
